16 Hours Ago “There is no destruction, so we haven’t lost any record.” He however, noted that the only damage to the data centre was the exterior, which houses the cooling units. Agba said one of the immediate steps taken was to shut down the data centre since the cooling units were no longer working optimally. He added that a full scale investigation would be instituted to ascertain the cause of the incident.